{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6f5fb3314a","title":"中央《关于学习周恩来同志政府工作报告的通知》","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a72da77bd0","type":"title","text":"中央《关于学习周恩来同志政府工作报告的通知》","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6f5fb3314a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"349d740d7f","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘引）（一九六五年一月十四日）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6f5fb3314a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4cd31fa1ed","type":"paragraph","text":"外国一切好的经验，好的科学技术，我们都吸收过来，为我们所用。拒绝向外国学习是不对的，当然迷信外国，认为外国的东西都是好的，也是不对的，不论是迷信苏联，还是迷信西方，都不对，正确的态度应当是尊重科学，破除迷信。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6f5fb3314a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a4ce2f005","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6f5fb3314a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f0b52dce55","type":"paragraph","text":"引进新技术不是一味摹仿，照抄照搬。学习外国必须用独创精神，结合起来，引进技术必须同自己钻研结合起来。对于进口的技术装备，必须加以研究，一般从仿制做起，进而结合我国的具体情况加以该进和提高。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6f5fb3314a","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":434,"end":433}}}},"__N_SSG":true}